Interface PiecesToStartingFormation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PieceGroup

    public interface PiecesToStartingFormation
    Provides methods to initialize a new start state for a chess game. Only needed by PieceGroup. This interface exists to make piecegroup's code more readable.
    Author:
    pyry
